OL,3,CFreeze on health budget proposed in
OL,4,CGuernsey
OL,6,FGuernsey's healthcare budget for 2026
OL,7,Fcould be frozen at its current level
OL,8,Fif an amendment is approved this week,
OL,9,Fwhich would cost the department #8
OL,10,Fmillion in extra funds.
OL,12,FHealth spending is set to rise by 3%
OL,13,Fin the budget as it now stands in
OL,14,FPolicy and Resources' plans for next
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FThat would take its budget to #261
OL,18,Fmillion, up from #253 million.
