OL,6,FHowever, Deputy Sloan says that with a
OL,7,Fmulti-million pound black hole in the
OL,8,Fisland's finances, Guernsey needs to
OL,9,F"live within its means" and health
OL,10,Fspending needs to be reined in if the
OL,11,Fisland wants to avoid "going broke".
OL,13,FHe said: "The thing is with health
OL,14,Fexpenditure is when I came to the
OL,15,Fisland in 2008, it was around #100
OL,16,Fmillion.
OL,18,F"Next year it's projected to be more
OL,19,Fthan #260 million and we can't keep
OL,20,Fincreasing health expenditure at
OL,21,Finfinitum, we just can't afford it."
