OL,6,FDeputy Sloan also wants to freeze the
OL,7,Fbudgets of Environment and
OL,8,FInfrastructure and Home Affairs in
OL,9,Fline with 2025 projections.
OL,11,FThe President of Health and Social
OL,12,FCare, Deputy George Oswald, said in
OL,13,Fresponse: "Last Saturday, my wife
OL,14,Fcollapsed at home with no pulse.
OL,16,F"The response from the ambulance, the
OL,17,FICU and everyone at HSC has been
OL,18,Fexemplary. We need to preserve that
OL,19,Fservice - we don't know who will be
OL,20,Faffected next".
