OL,6,FAmong the other amendments set to be
OL,7,Fdebated, Deputy Jayne Ozanne wants to
OL,8,Freduce the increase in fuel duty as
OL,9,Fproposed by Policy and Resources.
OL,11,FInstead of a 4.3% rise, she wants to
OL,12,Fsee it at 2.3%.
OL,14,FShe said: "I am very concerned that
OL,15,Finflation is hitting poorer islanders
OL,16,Fthe hardest and feel we must take
OL,17,Fmeasures that can support them where
OL,18,Fwe can.
