OL,6,F"Those who are less affluent are far
OL,7,Fless likely to be able to afford
OL,8,Felectric vehicles and are also far
OL,9,Fmore likely to be driving older cars,
OL,10,Fwhich are less fuel efficient and so
OL,11,Fuse more petrol."
OL,13,FDeputy Aidan Matthews also wants to
OL,14,Fkeep the level of tax relief islanders
OL,15,Fpay on mortgage interest payments to
OL,16,F#3,500, instead of it being reduced to
OL,17,F#2,500.
OL,19,FThe full list of amendments to the
OL,20,F2026 budget will be debated in the
OL,21,FGuernsey States this week.
